0. make softlink of input root files

=============================================================
1. make a .list file to list all full paths of the input
   root files
-------------------------------------------------------------
$ ls -1 /data7/xueliang/eRD11/eic_rich/modular_rich/likelihood/input/G4_data/*root > G4_data.list

=============================================================
2. rename all input root files by number using Split.C
-------------------------------------------------------------
change arguments in Split.C :
  1. number of .list file
  2. directory of output files

$ root Split.C
